// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2670 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: a8acb75d-2bd0-52c2-89d7-88f50cf29d56

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
